  "label": "Cot-Niche Alcove",
  "description": "Cot-Niche Alcove forms the sleep recess of Riftward Sleepcell, a narrow bay cast in black slagcrete and faced with scuffed vitrified panels. A recessed cot is locked into the structure beneath a grit-proof louvered light strip, its illumination tuned to the bastion’s regulated low-glow standard. Vox-shielding mesh and exposed conduit runs frame the alcove’s upper edge, muting the auroral backwash that stains the city’s nightside. Sealed lockers and a fabric-lined partition trap ash dust and leave a permanent tang of ozone in the confined air.",
